title: Journal
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Journal
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.

Journal may refer to:

  • Items named "Journal":
    • Journal (Creature of Fenkenstrain), an unobtainable item
    • Journal (Filliman Tarlock), Filliman Tarlock's instructions from Nature Spirit
    • Journal (Horror from the Deep), Jossik's account from Horror from the Deep
    • Journal (Making History), Drozal's book from Making History
  • Creature keeper's journal, obtained by searching the creature keeper
  • Dark journal, obtained from the chest upon defeating the Great Olm
  • Ebrill's journal, obtained from the Prifddinas Grand Library
  • Edern's journal, obtained by searching the dead guard in the Temple of Light's entrance
  • Feathered journal, obtained during Eagles' Peak
  • Glough's journal, obtained during The Grand Tree
  • Journal page, obtained in the Icyene Graveyard
  • Malumac's journal, obtained in the Karamjan Temple
  • Neilan's journal, obtained during Getting Ahead
  • Old journal, obtained during Underground Pass
  • Shayzien journal, obtained during A Kingdom Divided
  • Smelly journal, obtained in the Fishing Hamlet
  • Soggy journal, obtained from the Prifddinas Grand Library
  • Stained journal, obtained from the Prifddinas Grand Library
  • Tekton's journal, obtained upon defeating Tekton
  • Tree wizards' journal, obtained from chests in the Shade Catacombs

See also[edit | edit source]

  • Diary
